text: Chauvetia obliqua is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. This name is considered a nomen dubium ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Segers W., Swinnen F. & De Prins R., 2009. Marine Molluscs of Madeira. Snoeck Publishers, Heule, Belgium, 612 p. ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1979
